<h1>Best Movies of 2017</h1>

<h2>Getting Started</h2>
	To run the project locally, execute the file called entertainment_center.py with the command 		python entertainment_center.py

<h3>Prerequisites:</h3>
	python 2.7

<h3>Installation of prerequisites:</h3>
	On Ubuntu, on the terminal run command sudo apt install python2.7 python-pip
	On Windows, go to https://www.python.org/downloads/windows/
	On MacOS, go to https://www.python.org/downloads/mac-osx/

<h3>To run this project:</h3>
	Clone the directory https://github.com/vicentedpsantos/best-movies-list.git
	Navigate to the directory cd repository_name
	Run python entertainment_center.py
	
	On IDLE:
	Open IDLE
	Open file entertainment_center.py
	In the menu bar click on Run -> Run Module or press F5 on your keyboard

<h3>Built With</h3>
	Python IDLE
	CSS, Bootstrap
	JavaScript, JQuery

<h1>Authors</h3>
